UPDATE faqs SET answer = 'Yes, there are third-party charges. Aura Intercept never resells or bundles provider usage. SignalWire (voice/SMS), ElevenLabs (AI voice), Resend (email), and Tavily (AI search) each bill you directly through your own provider account and credit card on file. Your Aura plan covers the platform only; provider usage is pay-as-you-go (including during the 60-Day Live Trial) with no Aura markup.' WHERE question = 'Are there extra fees for SMS, voice, or email?';